      *                  * Riciclo                                     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     exe-exp-vpr-640.
       exe-exp-vpr-648.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Ciclo di scansione                          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-exe-ctr-001          .
       exe-exp-vpr-650.
           add       1                    to   w-exe-ctr-001          .
           if        w-exe-ctr-001        >    03
                     go to exe-exp-vpr-658.
