      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Sel su [yvp]                                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Solo definizioni                            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        rf-yvp-cod-dpz       not  = zero
                     go to exe-exp-yvp-200.
       exe-exp-yvp-500.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Incremento numero records letti                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   inc-rec-let-000      thru inc-rec-let-999        .
           if        w-exe-flg-brk        not  = spaces
                     go to exe-exp-yvp-800.
       exe-exp-yvp-550.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
